區 就要以 <span style=\"color: red;\">電匯</span>方式 (網上銀行會見到) 收費相對貴<br />\n<br />\n如果匯款銀行無同收款銀行有直接聯繫 會再經由中間銀行匯款 會另外再收一筆費用 <br />\n<br />\n而本身匯款行同收款行都會收取費用的"},{"pid":"712596810e6a5556910209b8a79396e689f93e64","tid":1870563,"uid":161177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24e11d0ec2884ec9854bcd2b0d27f597dd4a9c7","tid":1870563,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"853f6b7a668e1104882ad405c77738fa5208c577","tid":1870563,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"電匯 online banking做到 會收手續費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"網上電匯需要申請？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"一般銀行會有個 token 可以做無登記匯款 但limit較低<br />\n有機會需要係設定調整限額先<br />\n<br />\n而你如果匯多d既 就要登記收款人 但網上一般需要時間處理申請/必須到銀行申請(視乎銀行)"},{"pid":"e4ef2f853bfcbb5738733f5e55ae715d9cb5eeb6","tid":1870563,"uid":161177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81d6b85afe38afd36d11fc0d1ac751d983405ae9","tid":1870563,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"多數幾耐先匯到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"Chats 大多可以於銀行工作天即日到帳<br />\n匯款 視乎地區 (大陸1-2天)<br />\n以上假設是正常交易"},{"pid":"83bb4dcec1aed96feb3c8b2ed49f23f46a24f750","tid":1870563,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"邊間銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D銀行有D戶口唔洗嫁"},{"pid":"efdefb5208fdfe79703733f2e3c99179f0627a72","tid":1870563,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bf97c6768f4e3853bba3e85d8ebf6588efd839b","tid":1870563,"uid":161177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1b09be7523e465a2218f71041d0ddc66567bd4","tid":1870563,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲知 想係A銀行外幣轉去B銀行要點搞？網上銀行搞唔搞到？"},"citedB